e_date":"2010-10-23","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Marea Baja","original_language":"es"},{"id":49014,"adult":false,"title":"Cosmopolis","video":false,"overview":"Riding across Manhattan in a stretch limo during a riot in order to get a haircut, a 28-year-old billionaire asset manager's life begins to crumble.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":1.4043,"vote_count":1319,"poster_path":"/94m7J9YeO0W7IEbfsOtFbweGgcu.jpg","release_date":"2012-05-25","vote_average":5.7,"backdrop_path":"/g2MHMRGMqBMHAdDmnB2QFynT0WN.jpg","original_title":"Cosmopolis","original_language":"en"},{"id":49021,"adult":false,"title":"Killer Elite","video":false,"overview":"Based on a shocking true story, Killer Elite pits two of the world’s most elite operatives—Danny, an ex-special ops agent and Hunter, his longtime mentor—against the cunning leader of a secret military society. Covering the globe from Australia to Paris, London and the Middle East, Danny and Hunter are plunged into a highly dangerous game of cat and mouse—where the predators become the prey.","genre_ids":[28,12,53],"popularity":3.2226,"vote_count":2269,"poster_path":"/7O2U0WPFPSvNSUYZlhbnV081lBF.jpg","release_date":"2011-09-22","vote_average":6.264,"backdrop_path":"/RzIuQRoXiO8WeFdjtnjUCzSymV.jpg","original_title":"Killer Elite","original_language":"en"},{"id":49026,"adult":false,"title":"The Dark Knight Rises","video":false,"overview":"Following the death of District Attorney Harvey Dent, Batman assumes responsibility for Dent's crimes to protect the late attorney's reputation and is subsequently hunted by the Gotham City Police Department. Eight years later, Batman encounters the mysterious Selina Kyle and the villainous Bane, a new terrorist leader who overwhelms Gotham's finest. The Dark Knight resurfaces to protect a city that has branded him an enemy.","genre_ids":[28,80,18,53],"popularity":15.4056,"vote_count":24020,"poster_path":"/hr0L2aueqlP2BYUblTTjmtn0hw4.jpg","release_date":"2012-07-17","vote_ave